267
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:50,920
Yan Xing,

268
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:53,720
I, Shen Du, am exactly this kind of person.

269
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,600
Great Chief,

270
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:12,360
I truly feel injustice on your behalf.

271
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:13,680
The fact that woman is not content
is one thing.

272
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,200
But she even turns out to be
a fierce and evil woman.

273
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:17,200
At the beginning, she at least pretended a bit.

274
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:20,000
