279
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,920
Jing Lin,

280
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,200
well,

281
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,600
is it that Mrs. Shen was beaten by her husband

282
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:37,920
or is it that the White Ghost
met a female demon

283
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,960
could excite the ladies

284
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:41,640
of Xiang'an City even more

285
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,640
and make the likes of Prime Minister Zhang

286
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:47,080
feel that there's an opportunity to exploit?

287
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:50,800
Several days have passed since the wedding day.

288
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:53,720
It must provide some fodder for gossip.

289
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:00,880
You mean it's intentional
to let those with ulterior motives

290
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:01,920
