293
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:10,040
So the quarrel you had today

294
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:12,160
was deliberate?

295
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,800
Clever indeed.

296
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:16,480
The injuries on Madam

297
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:19,120
were also inflicted by design?

298
