for the poor scholars throughout the land?

336
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,720
You have misunderstood.

337
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:10,160
Princess of Valor,

338
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:13,640
who do you think would be more suitable?

339
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,600
I think

340
