368
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,520
Alright.

369
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:20,200
About this matter,

370
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:23,000
let me think about it.

371
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:28,600
I take my leave.

